Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Software Engineer position with Relativity. I bring over three years of professional experience in scalable distributed systems, serverless architectures, and cloud-native platforms, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

