nd serverless technologies to handle long-running data import jobs and prevent AWS Lambda timeouts — both of which required the systems-level thinking, quality focus, and operational stability that this role demands. Together, these roles have prepared me to contribute meaningfully to building performant, scalable, and secure software on Relativity's highly scalable and dynamic web system and serverless technologies.

