I have always been passionate about truth, transparency, and helping organizations discover the truth from their data, and envision myself contributing my talent to the furthering of Relativity's mission to help customers organize data, discover the truth, and act on it. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

